Bubble Sort

      

      

      
Time Complexity:

      

      
Worst Case:      O(n2)

      
Average Case:  O(n2)

      
Best Case:        O(n )

      

      
Code (Java):

      

      
{"void bubbleSort(int[] arr) {                "} 

      
{"   int n = arr.length;                       "} 

      
{"   // for each element in the array"} 

      
{"   for(int i=0; i < n-1; i++) {              "} 

      
{"       // for each element after the i"} 

      
{"       for(int j=0; j < (n-i)-1; j++) {        "} 

      
{"         // if next element is smalleer than current"} 

      
{"           if(arr[j] > arr[j+1]) {               "} 

      
{"               swap(arr, j, i);                    "} 

      
{"           }                                     "} 

      
{"       }                                      "} 

      
{"   }                                        "}
